                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9495" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2362</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">971 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鼎故革新，与时偕行——武汉钢铁有限公司绿色低碳的战略转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Reform and innovation, keeping up with the times: the road of green and low-carbon strategic transformation of Wuhan Iron and Steel Co., Ltd</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邓新明，刘新韬，覃谊，叶震宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国宝武武钢集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">24 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色低碳；战略转型；武钢有限</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Green and Low-carbon; Strategic Transformation；Wuhan Iron and Steel Co.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以武钢有限绿色低碳的战略转型历程为线索，完整梳理了武钢有限成立前后的绿色低碳发展背景及行动举措，分阶段讲述了其绿色低碳的战略转型变化。武钢有限作为中国宝武集团的核心生产企业，是国家地区经济社会发展的重要支撑，担负着重任。而如今“双碳”目标的提出给钢铁行业带来了前所未有的挑战，产能产量的限制，能耗和碳排放“双控”要求不断提高，出口退税取消及碳边境税的出现增加了出口阻碍，产业链发生巨大变化，同行业竞争日益激烈，有效控制成本、提高经营效益难度极大，“高排放、高能耗、高污染”的标签也已经在武钢有限的身上贴附很久。这一系列的问题困扰着武钢有限的发展，在这样的发展背景下，绿色低碳战略转型迫在眉睫。从2012年开始碳管理进行绿色低碳发展的初步探索，到2016年宝武重组后开始新的起点，进行绿色低碳发展的融合，再到2020年“双碳”目标提出后绿色低碳发展的全面延伸，最后到绿色低碳发展的未来展望，这一路上武钢有限取得了一系列绿色低碳战略转型的重要成果。
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case takes the green and low-carbon strategic transformation process of Wuhan Iron and Steel Co., Ltd as a clue, completely reviews the green and low-carbon development background and action measures before and after the establishment of Wuhan Iron and Steel Co., Ltd, and describes its green and low-carbon strategic transformation changes in stages. As the core production enterprise of China Baowu Group, Wuhan Iron and Steel Co., Ltd is an important support for regional economic and social development and shoulder heavy responsibilities. Nowadays, the goal of &quot;double carbon&quot; has brought unprecedented challenges to the iron and steel industry. The limitation of production capacity and output, the increasing requirement of &quot;double control&quot; of energy consumption and carbon emissions, the cancellation of export tax rebate and the emergence of carbon border tax have increased export obstacles, great changes have taken place in the industrial chain, and the competition in the same industry has become increasingly fierce. It is very difficult to effectively control costs and improve operating efficiency. The label of &quot;high emission, high energy consumption and high pollution&quot; has also been attached to Wuhan Iron and Steel Co., Ltd for a long time. This series of problems plaguing the development of Wuhan Iron and Steel Co., Ltd. Under such a development background, green and low-carbon strategic transformation is imminent. The initial exploration of green and low-carbon development started from carbon management in 2012, and then started a new starting point for the integration of green and low-carbon development after the reorganization of Baowu in 2016, and then fully extended green and low-carbon development after the &quot;double carbon&quot; goal was proposed in 2020, and finally the future outlook of green and low-carbon development. Along the way, Wuhan Iron and Steel Co., Ltd has achieved a series of important results of green and low-carbon strategic transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略转型理论；制度逻辑理论；差异化战略理论；价值链分析；绿色创新理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
